            <p>I will send only a line this time&#8212;as I have written to Herb at some length, &#38; <choice><abbr>ab't</abbr><expan>about</expan></choice> in response to yours the same&#8212;Best love to you as always. I will keep you posted, dear friend, of any literary utterance or personal news&#8212;</p>

            <closer>
                <signed rend="right">Walt Whitman</signed>
            </closer>
        </body>
